dmca_clarifications: We have over 500,000 different artist pages. Our site  
has been live for more than two years. This is the first and only DMCA  
complaint we have ever had.

We never received any notification as to why the page was in violation of  
the DMCA so we were not sure how to correct it. We decided to remove the  
page completely. We trust that removing the page resolved any copyright  
issues.

We are ready & willing to take the necessary action to maintain our good  
standing.
